function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_PRAVA, CONVO_PRAVA)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_PRAVA, 1.5)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_PRAVA)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_VIGO_EXIT, ID_VIGO_PRAVA)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_VIGO_PRAVA, CONVO_VIGO_EXIT)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_VIGO_PRAVA, LOC_VIGO_EXIT, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_VIGO_PRAVA)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ID_VIGO_PRAVA, 1)
	Hydra.EventSend("COMPLETE")
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	followerVigo = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_VIGO_FOLLOWER)
	
	--Vigo Bark / Guard Move / Door Open / Guard Bark
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_VIGO_GUARD_01, followerVigo)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerVigo, CONVO_VIGO_GUARD_01)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerVigo)
	end
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_GUARD, LOC_GUARD, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_GUARD, LOC_GUARD)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_GUARD)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(ID_INVIS_DOOR)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(ID_PRAVA_DOOR)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_VIGO_GUARD_02, ID_GUARD)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_GUARD,CONVO_VIGO_GUARD_02)
			
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	followerVigo = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_VIGO_FOLLOWER)
	
	--Prava Ambient Convo
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_PRAVA_AMBIENT, ID_PRAVA)
	
	--Vigo Move Action
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerVigo) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerVigo, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerVigo)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerVigo, LOC_VIGO_PRAVA, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerVigo, LOC_VIGO_PRAVA)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(followerVigo)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_VIGO_PRAVA)
	Hydra.EventSend("KV1_PRAVA")
	
end
